nhc_headline: ...TROPICAL DEPRESSION FIFTEEN-E FORMS WELL TO THE SOUTH-SOUTHWEST OF BAJA CALIFORNIA...
summary: ...TROPICAL DEPRESSION FIFTEEN-E FORMS WELL TO THE SOUTH-SOUTHWEST OF BAJA CALIFORNIA... As of 2:00 AM MST Tue Sep 30 the center of Fifteen-E was located near 9.4, -113.2 with movement WNW at 5 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1005 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 35 mph.
